name: Alpha Authority Veterans
description:
Recognizing Alpha Authority's Veterans, joining this group gets you special perks in-game, on site, in our main community server, news to unreleased developments, and access to AA's private archives via disc. Going back to 2012, AA is a historic war clan in the ROBLOX Clans & Guilds Community. In preservation, and the protection of the sacred world, Empress ScriptIntelligence has made efforts at making the largest archive network for the AA Community. The fabric that makes up AA's world is connected to here, and your view of how large this group was will change forever by going through this page.

This Group is a Work In Progress. AA Veteran's Club is welcome to all Veterans, please join if you are one!
